I havn't been posting lately, but that's cause I'm typing away at the comp, coding this new login system. The code from the current one isn't too good for the remake, so I'm writing brand new code. I am almost done setting up the database for it.

I have recieved very little responce to my suggestion of moving everything to the NBW site. Does anyone care other than the 5 or 6 people that replied? If you do, speak up!

Also, and thanks to Airly for reminding me of this, Moonmist emailed me saying that she can't participate anymore. She said someone could take her chars. Anyone want them? I already have some requests for 'em.
